  "prompt": "What does \"AAA\" mean in AAA title game?",
  "response": "In the context of video games, \"AAA\" refers to high-budget, high-quality games that are typically produced and published by large, well-established companies. These games often involve significant investment in development, marketing, and production, and they are expected to have a high level of polish, extensive content, and broad appeal. \"AAA\" is analogous to blockbuster movies in the film industry.",
